Cheats
Cheater 2005
12.10.2005

Invisibility: 
Pause the game and press R1, L1, L1, R2, L1, L1, L2. 

Lighter cars: 
Pause the game and press L1, R1, R1, L2, R2, R2. 

No gravity: 
Pause the game and press R1, R2, R1, R2, Up, Up, Up. 

Increase time warp: 
Pause the game and press R1, L1, L2, R2, Right, Right, Right. 

Decrease time warp: 
Pause the game and press R2, L2, L1, R1, Left, Left, Left.  